Implementation Summary
----------------------
- Implemented `find_project_root(start_path: Path | None = None) -> Path`
  - Walks up directory tree from start_path (default: CWD)
  - Finds nearest `project.godot` file
  - Raises `ConfigError` if not found at filesystem root

- Implemented `load_config(project_root: Path | None = None) -> GdToolsConfig`
  - Discovers project root via `find_project_root()` if not provided
  - Reads `gd-tools.toml` from project root
  - Returns `GdToolsConfig()` defaults if file missing (no error)
  - Uses `tomllib` (Python 3.11+) with `tomli` backport for 3.10
  - Catches `TOMLDecodeError` → raises `ConfigError` with file path
  - Catches Pydantic `ValidationError` → raises `ConfigError` with details

